Package ubikloadpack.jmeter.ulp.observability.listener

Class ULPObservabilityListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jmeter.testelement.AbstractTestElement
      • ubikloadpack.jmeter.ulp.observability.listener.ULPObservabilityListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, org.apache.jmeter.engine.util.NoThreadClone, org.apache.jmeter.gui.Searchable, org.apache.jmeter.samplers.SampleListener, org.apache.jmeter.testelement.TestElement, org.apache.jmeter.testelement.TestStateListener
    public class ULPObservabilityListener
extends org.apache.jmeter.testelement.AbstractTestElement
implements org.apache.jmeter.samplers.SampleListener, org.apache.jmeter.testelement.TestStateListener, org.apache.jmeter.engine.util.NoThreadClone, java.io.Serializable
    A class for listening and exposing extended JMeter metrics this class extends AbstractTestElement to define it as a test element and implements : SampleListener: to be notified each time a sample occurred; TestStateListener : to be notified each time a test started or ended; NoThreadClone : to use the same thread for all samples, in an other way to disable cloning the tread for each sample; Includes embedded Jetty server, sample registry and logger.
